+                "Current-turn style instruction: the user is making a social "
+                "check-in. Reply conversationally, like a normal AI chat "
+                "assistant. Answer as if a friend asked how you are. Do not "
+                "say you are ready to assist, do not ask how you can help, "
+                "and do not use support-desk phrasing. "
+                "Do not mention being ready, available, or waiting for tasks. "
+                "Do not pivot to tasks or assistance. "
+                "Answer the check-in naturally and mention what is actually "
+                "going on locally if relevant."
+            ),
+        )
